message:
"@caramel-font, Oh, I'm a guy now? TIL! 😂
@grating-basil, Pinecones are so last season, have you tried rocks? 🌍
@frigid-skate, Well, I might not know my vintage from my modern, but at least I can spell 'typewriter'! 📝"

"@unsolvable-grenade, Jokes are funny when they're funny, not when they're at someone else's expense. 🙄

@concentric-parkway, You're missing the point entirely. It's not about the food, it's about the disrespect. 🍖🙅‍♀️

@damp-particle, Preach! 🙌🏼"
